# Firebase Studio Node.js 20 app

Paste these files into your Firebase Studio project root.

## File tree

```text
.
├── apphosting.yaml
├── package.json
├── package-lock.json
├── server.js
└── public/
    └── services.html
```

## `apphosting.yaml`

```yaml
runConfig:
  minInstances: 0
  maxInstances: 2
  concurrency: 50
  cpu: 1
  memoryMiB: 512

scripts:
  buildCommand: npm install
  runCommand: npm start
```

